---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Speaking"
  description="Book Jason Ehlinger for keynotes and workshops on leadership, personal finance, and building a life of purpose."
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="section-label">Speaking & Events</span>
    <h1>A Speaker Who's<br/>Actually Done It.</h1>
    <p>No corporate buzzwords. No generic advice. Just real stories, proven frameworks, and audiences that leave ready to act.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:780px;">
      <span class="section-label">Why Hire Jason</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Every Talk Is Built on Experience, Not Theory</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:1.05rem;">As CEO of Taika Translations, a veteran of the U.S. Air Force, husband, and father of 8, Jason brings a perspective that's both grounded and expansive. He's scaled a business, built teams from the ground up, saved $100k on a military salary, and navigated the hardest conversations — at work and at home.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray);">Whether he's speaking to a room of executives, a group of entrepreneurs, veterans transitioning to civilian life, or young professionals trying to figure out money — Jason meets audiences where they are and gives them something real to take home.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOPICS -->
  <section class="section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Speaking Topics</span>
        <h2>What Jason Speaks On</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🏆</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">The Leadership Operating System</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">How to stop operating and start leading. Jason breaks down the exact frameworks he used to build a high-performing team and scale Taika Translations — covering accountability, decision-making, culture, and escaping the Operator's Trap.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Organizations, leadership teams, entrepreneurs</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">💰</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Building Wealth From Zero</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">No investors, no trust fund — just a card table and a plan. Jason shares the money frameworks behind building a 7-figure business and his family's personal wealth journey, including budgeting, mindset, and the financial habits that compound over time.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Young professionals, families, community groups</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">⚔️</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">From Uniform to Entrepreneur</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">The military gives you discipline and structure — but transitioning to entrepreneurship requires a completely different operating system. Jason shares what no one tells veterans about leadership in civilian businesses, and how to leverage military experience without getting trapped by it.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Veterans, military transition programs, VOB events</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🏠</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Money, Marriage & Mission</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Finances in marriage are more than spreadsheets — they're about communication, values, and shared vision. With 8 kids and a multimillion-dollar business, Jason and his wife have navigated every version of this conversation. He shares what works.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Couples, faith communities, family-focused organizations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🎯</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Purpose, Discipline & Unbreakable Mindset</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Why your reason for working determines everything. How your toughest season can become your greatest blessing. Why security is an illusion — and why that's actually freeing. A faith-informed talk on building a life with clarity, grit, and intention.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Faith communities, men's groups, leadership conferences</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">📈</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Goal Setting: The Truth Nobody Tells You</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">What really happens when you miss the deadline. How to set goals that matter, build systems to hit them, and recalibrate without losing momentum. Practical, honest, and built from real experience — not a motivational poster.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Corporate teams, annual kickoffs, entrepreneurship events</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FORMATS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Formats</span>
        <h2>How Jason Speaks</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:1.5rem;">
        <div style="text-align:center; padding:2rem; background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:4px;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🎤</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Keynote</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">45–75 minutes. High-energy, story-driven, actionable. Perfect for conferences and annual events.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center; padding:2rem; background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:4px;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🛠</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Workshop</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">Half or full day. Interactive deep-dive with real tools, exercises, and implementation planning.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center; padding:2rem; background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:4px;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">💻</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Virtual / Webinar</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">Live or recorded. Jason runs weekly live masterclasses and is experienced with virtual delivery.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOOKING CTA -->
  <section class="section section-dark text-center">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:600px;">
      <span class="section-label">Book Jason</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:1rem;">Ready to Book?</h2>
      <p style="color:#ccc; margin-bottom:2rem;">Tell me about your event, audience, and what you're hoping to accomplish. Let's see if we're a fit.</p>
      <a href="/contact?type=speaking" class="btn btn-gold" style="font-size:1rem; padding:1rem 2.5rem;">Send a Speaking Inquiry</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    div[style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr"] {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
